	an InvalidCastException if the widening conversion failed. See
	testcases #M94-#M96.

	* Array.cs (CopyTo): Bug fix from Ajay Dwivedi, correctly handle
	arrays with non-zero lower bounds. Also adding testcases #F10-#F13
	for this.

